author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Neuca Q1 Net Profit Up At 31.8 Million Zlotys
text:
May 14 (Reuters) - NEUCA SA:
* Q1 NET PROFIT 31.8 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 30.2 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* Q1 EBITDA 48.3 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 47.2 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* Q1 REVENUE 2.16 BILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 2.00 BILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
